description: Lumpia World is a fusion of Filipino & Island Cuisine. Lumpia World markets and distributes various types of quality Lumpia. Customized to serve the needs of our various markets, Lumpia World is a family owned Specialty Food Vendor / Caterer. Lumpia World is Headquarted in Renton, Washington in a state-of-the-art commercial kitchen. Lumpia World takes pride in hand rolling each Lumpia with quality ingredients.MISSION STATEMENTAt Lumpia World, you are family and as family you are at home with us. Enjoy the Love and Passion we roll up in each Lumpia. Thank you for your support.
name: Lumpia World
